name: Sixgill XSOAR Content Pack
description: This XSOAR playbook is configured to run as a time triggered job that periodically adds bad indicators from Sixgill Darkfeed to SIEM blocklist. The playbook further adds a tag to each indicator that is successfully added to the blocklist. Using this tag one can easily identify and filter the indicators that are added to the blocklist.
author: ArpithaSrinivas
